Package c_coupon.sys.core.beans

The Beans Package consist of Classes defining Objects in order to deliver information from the Application to the DAO which translate those to SQL and JDBC Every major table have it's own Object.

Package c_coupon.sys.core.beans Description

The Beans Package consist of Classes defining Objects in order to deliver information from the Application to the DAO which translate those to SQL and JDBC Every major table have it's own Object. (Object Company have Company Table etc.)
